query:
SELECT 
    id,
    email,
    name,
    CASE 
        WHEN passwordHash IS NULL THEN 'SEM_SENHA'
        WHEN passwordHash LIKE '$2%' THEN 'BCRYPT'
        WHEN LENGTH(passwordHash) = 64 THEN 'SHA256'
        ELSE 'DESCONHECIDO'
    END as tipo_hash,
    LENGTH(passwordHash) as tamanho_hash,
    createdAt
FROM users
ORDER BY createdAt DESC
LIMIT 10;
